 them seperately</span><hr size=1> there coming from comparing a level 44 thane and a 41 skald and there usefullness both in RVR and PVE<br>
<br>
I would like to see the DD shouts have the same Range as the snare shout.<br>
that way we can actually provide some usefulness in keep defense althought not much due to the timer of our shouts but still a bit of a help and better than sittign waiting for the doors to fall.<br>
<br>
