<br>
Now, an AE spell that casts point blank will have a much better case with Mythic, after all its difficult to shout just at 1 person without effecting others. However, I think that if a thane's AE already does little damage, if we got it, it would do even less and therefore be totally useless, not only but as a lot of thanes do it will have unexperienced skalds just break our healers mezzes.<br>
<br>
I agree that we are totally useless at keep defence, but that is the only 1 are useless. Having said that, if you wait for the raiders to come up to the Lords room, you can still do good dmg to them.<br>
<br>
